# Strategies With Tableau: A College Food Choices Case Study

## Project Overview
This project analyzes college students' food choices using Tableau. The dashboard provides insights into eating habits, food preferences, and factors influencing food selection.

## Objectives
- Analyze food choice patterns.
- Identify healthy and unhealthy eating habits.
- Create interactive Tableau dashboards.
- Present insights using data visualization.

## Tools Used
- Tableau
- CSV Dataset
- GitHub

## Project Files
- Dataset (.csv)
- Tableau Workbook (.twb/.twbx)
- Dashboard Screenshots
- Project Report

## Conclusion
This project demonstrates how Tableau can be used to visualize and analyze food choice data for better decision-making.
